snippet.title: Helldivers 2 "The Story So Far" | PS5 & PC Games
snippet.description:
https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/helldivers-2/   https://store.steampowered.com/agecheck/app/553850/

Everything on every planet wants you dead.
Terminids – fuelled by raw instinct and fury. The Automaton Collective – coded for socialist violence.
Become a merciless paragon of democracy and show them all the true meaning of real freedom.
Fight for your families, for your friends… for Super Earth!
Launches 8 February.

#ps5 #ps5games #pcgames #helldivers2 

Rated Mature
